  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de FFmpeg</title>

    <para>Si vous n'avez pas installé <application>Xorg</application> dans
    <filename class='directory'>/usr</filename>, dîtes à <filename>configure</filename>
    ou le trouver:</para>
<screen><userinput>export LIBRARY_PATH=$XORG_PREFIX/lib</userinput></screen>

    <para>Installez <application>FFmpeg</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr        \
            --disable-debug      \
            --enable-shared      \
            --disable-static     \
            --enable-gpl         \
            --enable-x11grab     \
            --enable-postproc    \
            --enable-version3    \
            --enable-nonfree     \
            --enable-libfaac     \
            --enable-libfreetype \
            --enable-libmp3lame  \
            --enable-libopenjpeg \
            --enable-libspeex    \
            --enable-libtheora   \
            --enable-libvorbis   \
            --enable-libvpx      \
            --enable-libxvid     \
            --enable-libpulse    \
            --enable-openssl     &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

